messages	O
are	O
stored	O
in	O
the	O
memory	O
of	O
the	O
call	O
processing	O
subsystem	O
for	O
instructing	O
a	O
user	O
on	O
his	O
or	O
her	O
progress	O
in	O
using	O
the	O
system	O
.	O
