The	O
present	O
invention	O
has	O
numerous	O
advantages	O
over	O
the	O
Prior	O
art	O
.	O
The	O
system	O
combines	O
the	O
use	O
of	O
both	O
speaker-dependent	O
and	O
speaker-independent	O
speech	O
recognition	O
in	O
an	O
