and	O
less	O
sensitive	O
to	O
these	O
conditions	O
.	O
Adding	O
the	O
distorted	O
but	O
intelligible	O
data	O
to	O
the	O
training	O
database	O
of	O
excellent	O
example	O
words	O
allows	O
for	O
a	O
more	O
diverse	O
statistical	O
representation	O
of	O
each	O
vocabulary	O
word	O
.	O
Words	O
that	O
might	O
have	O
been	O
previously	O
rejected	O
,	O
because	O
