for	O
accurate	O
recognition	O
,	O
the	O
recognition	O
system	O
will	O
reject	O
the	O
word	O
and	O
reprompt	O
the	O
user	O
for	O
input	O
.	O

The	O
invention	O
also	O
enables	O
real-time	O
vocabulary	O
uploading	O
.	O
Previously	O
,	O
speech	O
recognition	O
